resourceInfo.abstract: The Confederated Salish and Kootenai Tribes (CSKT) will identify and implement the goals and objectives outlined in  CSKT Climate Change Strategic Plan.  This funding is part of a larger pool of resources to sustain and enhance the cultural, community, and conservation goals and values of the GNLCC. Through this effort the CSKT, its partners, and stakeholders will increase our understanding of regional and global climate change impacts. We will use our combined expertise and knowledge to help the people of the Flathead Nation and surrounding areas adapt and mitigate to climate impacts affecting us all.
